+// Append the local vertices whose order-1 nodal shape function is nonzero at
+// ip; these identify the minimal mesh entity (vertex/edge/face, or the whole
+// element) that ip lies on. The order-1 nodal element has one dof per vertex,
+// in vertex order, so shape(i) is the weight of vertex i. On-entity weights
